(1, 's1-teknologi-informasi', 'S1 – Teknologi Informasi', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Teknologi Informasi.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>004</strong> : Ilmu Komputer / teknologi Informasi</li><li><strong>004.019</strong> : Prinsip Psikologis dalam Ilmu Komputer</li><li><strong>372.35</strong> : Sains &amp; teknologi untuk pendidikan dasar</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Teknologi Informasi, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/search?searchTerm=information+technology#/title\"><strong>Biodiversity Heritage Library</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://bookboon.com/en/search?q=information+technology\"><strong>Bookboon.com</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.free-ebooks.net/search/information+technology\"><strong>Free-ebooks.net</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.freetechbooks.com/\"><strong>Freetechbooks</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://archive.org/search.php?query=information%20technology&amp;sin=TXT\"><strong>Internet Archive</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.onlineprogrammingbooks.com/information-technology/\"><strong>OnlineProgrammingbooks.com</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.pdfdrive.net/information-technology-books.html\"><strong>Pdfdrive.net</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/weed%20technology/listing?q=information+technology&amp;searchWithinIds=96F2DAEB1066989CF72064E97B1D8112\"><strong>APSIPA Transactions on Signal and Information Processing : cambrige</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://journal.acs.org.au/index.php/ajis/issue/archive\"><strong>Australasian Journal of Information Systems</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://doaj.org/\"><strong>Directory Of Open Access Journals</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.is.cityu.edu.hk/staff/isrobert/ejisdc.htm\"><strong>Electronic Journal of Information Systems in Developing Countries</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://humanit.hb.se/issue/archive\"><strong>Human IT</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournals.bc.edu/ojs/index.php/ital/issue/archive\"><strong>Information Technology and Libraries</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mirlabs.org/ijcisim/archives.php\"><strong>International Journal of Computer Information Systems and Industrial Management Applications</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://http//airccse.org/journal/ijitcs/archives.html\"><strong>International journal Of Information Technology Convergence and Service ( IJITCS)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jbiomedsem.biomedcentral.com/articles?query=information+technology&amp;searchType=journalSearch&amp;tab=keyword\"><strong>Journal of Biomedical Semantics</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.hindawi.com/search/all/information+technology/\"><strong>Journal of Computer Networks and Communications : Hindawi</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jios.foi.hr/index.php/jios/issue/archive\"><strong>Journal of Information and Organizational Sciences</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.josis.org/index.php/josis/issue/archive\"><strong>Journal of Spatial Information Science</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mdpi.com/\"><strong>MDPI</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mecs-press.org/search.html?search=information%20technology\"><strong>Modern Education and Computer Science Press</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.sciencedirect.com/search?qs=information+technology&amp;authors=&amp;pub=&amp;v