(4, 's1-pendidikan-bahasa-inggris', 'S1 - Pendidikan Bahasa Inggris', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Pendidikan Bahasa Inggris.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>420</strong> : English &amp; Old English</li><li><strong>421</strong> : English Writing System &amp; Phonology</li><li><strong>422</strong> : English Etymology</li><li><strong>423</strong> : English Dictionary</li><li><strong>425</strong> : English Grammar</li><li><strong>427</strong> : English Language Variations</li><li><strong>428</strong> : Standard English Usage</li><li><strong>429</strong> : Old English</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku bidang Pendidikan Bahasa Inggris, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"http://bookboon.com/en/i-still-cant-speak-english-ebook\"><strong>Bookboon</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.ebooks-for-all.com/bookmarks/list/onecat/Electronic-books+Literature-by-country+English-Literature/0.html\"><strong>E-Books for all</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://manybooks.net/titles/fletcherroetext058hist10.html\"><strong>Many Books</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://freebooks.pupilgarage.com/FreeBookDownload?category=english_literature\"><strong>Pupil Garage</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/search/?query=english+literature\"><strong>Project Gutenberg&nbsp;</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.forgottenbooks.com/en/download/EnglishLiterature_10205576.pdf\"><strong>Forgotten books</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.pdfdrive.net/\"><strong>Pdfdrive.net</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://jurnal.usk.ac.id/SiELE\"><strong>Jurnal SiELE</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://llt.msu.edu/issues/october2017/index.html\"><strong>Language Learning &amp; Technology</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.aclweb.org/portal/cljournal\"><strong>Association for compatutional linguistics</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.jowr.org/current.html\"><strong>Journal of Writing Research</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://ejournal.ukm.my/gema/issue/archive\"><strong>Gema Online</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.journals.aiac.org.au/index.php/IJALEL\"><strong>Ijalel</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://ejournals.ukm.my/3l\"><strong>Universiti Kebangsaan Malaysia</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.tandfonline.com/loi/rjls20\"><strong>Taylor Francis Online</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://ojs.ub.gu.se/ojs/index.php/njes/index\"><strong>Nourdic Journal of English Studies</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.skase.sk/jti.html\"><strong>Skase Jurnal</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.tewtjournal.org/\"><strong>Tewt Journal</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.uinjkt.ac.id/index.php/ijee\"><strong>Indonesian Journal Of English Education&nbsp;UIN Syarif</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://e-journal.hamzanwadi.ac.id/index.php/veles\"><strong>Universitas Hamzanwadi</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://ijeltal.org/index.php/ijeltal/issue/archive\"><strong>IAIN&nbsp;Samarinda</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://journal.uniku.ac.id/index.php/ERJEE\"><strong>Universitas Kuningan</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnal.unissula.ac.id/index.php/edulite/index\"><strong>Universitas Islam Sultan Agung</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://journal2.uad.ac.id/index.php/eltej\"><strong>Universitas Ahmad Dahlan</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnalfaktarbiyah.iainkediri.ac.id/index.php/jeels\"><stron