(9, 's1-tadris-matematika', 'S1 – Tadris Matematika', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Tadris Matematika.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>370</strong> : Pendidikan</li><li><strong>510</strong> : Matematika</li><li><strong>510.7</strong> : Pendidikan Matematika</li><li><strong>511</strong> : Prinsip Umum Matematika</li><li><strong>512</strong> : Aljabar</li><li><strong>513</strong> : Aritmatika</li><li><strong>515</strong> : Analisis, Kalkulus</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Tadris Matematika, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><p>1.&nbsp; Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Internasional, hampir semua jurnal berikut terindeks oleh Scopus:</p><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.ams.org/journals/bull/all_issues.html\"><strong>American mathematical society</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.acadsci.fi/mathematica/\"><strong>Annales academia scientiarum fennica mathematica</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mdpi.com/2297-8747/22/1\"><strong>Mathematical and Computational Applications</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.hindawi.com/search/all/mathematics/\"><strong>Hindawi &nbsp;</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://journals.tubitak.gov.tr/math/lastIssue.htm\"><strong>Tubitak academic journal</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://http//www.math.armstrong.edu/faculty/budden/journals.html\"><strong>Mathematics journal with online open access</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.omicsonline.org/physical-mathematics.php\"><strong>Journal of physical mathematics</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journals4free.com/?fq=class:mat&amp;fq=language:eng&amp;fq=spec:mathe\"><strong>Journal for free</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.sciencedirect.com/search?qs=mathematics&amp;pub=Advances%20in%20Mathematics&amp;show=25&amp;sortBy=relevance&amp;publicationTitles=272585&amp;accessTypes=openaccess&amp;lastSelectedFacet=accessTypes\"><strong>Science direct</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.epj.org/component/solr/?task=results#!q=mathematics&amp;sort=score%20desc&amp;rows=10&amp;f=language%3A%22en%22\"><strong>Epj.org</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://academic.oup.com/amrx/issue/2009/2\"><strong>Applied mathematics research express</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.springeropen.com/collections/rpdde-2014\"><strong>Springer open</strong></a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;2.&nbsp;Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Nasional:</p><ul><li><a href=\"http://jurnal.unpad.ac.id/jmi/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Matematika Integratif</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jms.fmipa.itb.ac.id/ojs_3.0.2/index.php/jms/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Matematika dan Sains</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.jims-a.org/index.php/jimsa/issue/archive\"><strong>Journal of the Indonesian Mathematical Society</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://journals.itb.ac.id/index.php/jmfs/issue/archive\"><strong>Journal of Mathematical and Fundamental Sciences</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"http://bookboon.com/en/statistics-and-mathematics-ebooks\"><strong>BookBoon.com</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.oapen.org/search?keyword=mathematics;f1-language=English;f2-subject=Mathematics%20and%20science::Mathematics\"><strong>Oapen open access</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Encyclopedias</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Image_(mathematics)#Image_of_an_element\"><strong>Wikipedia</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780195300826.001.0001/acref-9780195300826\"><strong>Oxford reference</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.encyclopediaofmath.org/index.php/Special:AllPages\"><strong>Encyclopedia of mathematics</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Dictionaries</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://fansmatematika.wordpress.com/2012/10/19/fans-matematika/\"><strong>Fansmatematika&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://naabil.com/kbbi/matematika\"><strong>Nabil.com</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.kamusq.com/2013/06/matematika-adalah-pengertian-dan.html\"><strong>Kamus Q</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Scholarships</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.studylondon.ac.uk/scholarships/search?keywords=mathematics&amp;qualification=&amp;country=&amp;subject=\"><strong>Study london official universiti guide</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Awards</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"http://famous-mathematicians.org/top-awards-in-mathematics/\"><strong>Top awards in mathematics</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.ams.org/profession/prizes-awards/ams-supported/nas-award\"><strong>American mathematical society</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.wfnmc.org/awards.html\"><strong>World federation of national mathenatics competitions</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mathunion.org/general/prizes\"><strong>IMU awards and prizes</strong></a></li></ul>', '2024-12-18 06:01:48', '2025-12-06 15:29:03'),
(10, 's1-komunikasi-dan-penyiaran-islam', 'S1 – Komunikasi dan Penyiaran Islam', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Komunikasi dan Penyiaran Islam.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li>2X7 : Pendidikan &amp; Dakwah</li><li>2X8 : Komunikasi Dakwah</li><li>2X8.2 : Penyiaran Islam</li><li>2X8.3 : Media Islam</li><li>2X8.4 : Jurnalistik Islam</li><li><strong>302.2</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;: Komunikasi antar pribadi</li><li><strong>304.23</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;:&nbsp;Hubungan antar manusia</li><li><strong>371.102 2</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;: Communication in Teaching</li><li><strong>372.6&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;: Communication Skills</li><li><strong>658.8</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;: Komunikasi pemasaran</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Komunikasi dan Penyiaran Islam, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><p>1.&nbsp; Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Internasional, hampir semua jurnal berikut terindeks oleh Scopus:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.cogitatiopress.com/mediaandcommunication/issue/archive\"><strong>Media and Communication Journal</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jcom.sissa.it/archive\"><strong>JCOM Journal of Science Communication</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.essachess.com/index.php/jcs/issue/archive\"><strong>ESSACHESS - Journal for Communication Studies</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://ijoc.org/index.php/ijoc/issue/archive\"><strong>IJOC International Journal of Communication</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://platformjmc.com/issues/\"><strong>Platform</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.gmj.uottawa.ca/current-issue_e.html\"><strong>Global Media Journal Canadian</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.mii.lt/informatics_in_education/contents.htm\"><strong>Informatics In Education</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.revistacomunicar.com/index.php?contenido=revista&amp;numero=actual\"><strong>Comunicar journal</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.triple-c.at/index.php/tripleC/issue/archive\"><strong>TripleC: Communication, Capitalism &amp; Critique</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.nordicom.gu.se/sv/publikationer/nordicom-review/all-issues\"><strong>Nordicom Review</strong></a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;2.&nbsp;Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Nasional:</p><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.e-jurnal.com/2013/09/jurnal-penelitian-komunikasi.html\"><strong>Jurnal Hasil Riset</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://jurnalaspikom.org/index.php/aspikom/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Aspikom</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://jurnalilkom.uinsby.ac.id/index.php/jurnalilkom/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Ilmu Komunikasi UIN Sunan ampel</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ojs.uajy.ac.id/index.php/jik/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Ilmu Komunikasi Universitas Atma Jaya</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://ejournal.undip.ac.id/index.php/interaksi/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Ilmu Komunikasi Interaksi UNDIP</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.unri.ac.id/index.php/JKMS/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Ilmu Komunikasi UNRI</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnal.kominfo.go.id/index.php/komunika/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal KOMUNIKA</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://studentjournal.petra.ac.id/index.php/ilmu-komunikasi/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal E-Komunikasi</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://ejournal.uin-suka.ac.id/isoshum/profetik/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Komunikasi Profetik</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://ojs.umsida.ac.id/index.php/kanal/issue/archive\"><strong>KANAL Jurnal Ilmu Komunikasi</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.oapen.org/search?keyword=communications\"><strong>Oapen Open Access</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.bookrix.com/search;keywords:communication,searchoption:books.html\"><strong>BookRix</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.intechopen.com/search?q=communications\"><strong>IntechOpen</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.free-management-ebooks.com/skills-communication.htm\"><strong>Free Management Book</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.pdfdrive.net/search?q=communication+science&amp;pagecount=&amp;sortby=&amp;searchin=en&amp;r=1\"><strong>PDFDrive</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Encyclopedias</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.britannica.com/topic/communication\"><strong>Encyclopedia Britannic</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.newworldencyclopedia.org/entry/Communication\"><strong>New World Encyclopedia</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://https//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Communication\"><strong>Wikipedia</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.thecanadianencyclopedia.ca/en/article/communications/\"><strong>Canadian Encyclopedia</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Dictionaries</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/communication\"><strong>Merriam Webste</strong></a><a href=\"https://fansmatematika.wordpress.com/2012/10/19/fans-matematika/\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780199568758.001.0001/acref-9780199568758\"><strong>Oxford Reference</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.jyu.fi/viesti/verkkotuotanto/ci/glossary.shtml\"><strong>Glossary of Communication</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Glossary_of_communication_disorders\"><strong>Wikipedia</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Scholarships</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.scholarships.com/financial-aid/college-scholarships/scholarships-by-%20%20major/communications-scholarships/\"><strong>Scolarship.com</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.collegescholarships.com/major-degree/communications-scholarships\"><strong>College Scholarhip</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://http//www.bestvalueschools.com/communications-scholarships/\"><strong>Best Value school</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Awards</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.terrapinn.com/awards/world-communication-awards/index.stm\"><strong>World Communications Award</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.terrapinn.com/awards/asia-communication-awards/\"><strong>Asia Communications Awards</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.ppa.co.uk/events\"><strong>PPA Awards</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.capio.org/excellence-in-communications-awards\"><strong>Capio</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.communicatorawards.com/\"><strong>Communicator awards</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.smps.org/mca/\"><strong>Marketing Communications Awards</strong></a></li></ul>', '2024-12-18 06:08:38', '2025-12-07 07:50:22'),
(11, 's1-farmasi', 'S1 – Farmasi', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Farmasi.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>615</strong> &nbsp; : Farmakologi dan Terapi</li><li><strong>615.1</strong> : Obat-obatan Materi Medika</li><li><strong>615.13</strong> : Formula Obat, Perumusan Obat</li><li><strong>615.14</strong> : Penulisan Resep Obat</li><li><strong>615.18</strong> : Teknik Pemeliharaan Obat</li><li><strong>615.19</strong> : Kimia Farmasi</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Farmasi, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.pdfdrive.net/pharmacy-books.html\"><strong>Pdf Drive.net</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://bookboon.com/en/search?q=pharmacy\"><strong>Bookboon.com</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.freebookcentre.net/medical_books_download/Pharmacy-On-Line-%5bEnglish%5d.html\"><strong>Free ebook.net</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.ebook3000.com/plus/search.php?keyword=pharmacy&amp;x=0&amp;y=0\"><strong>eBook3000</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.tradepub.com/?q=pharmacy&amp;\"><strong>TradePub</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mdpi.com/2226-4787/5/4/55\"><strong>MDPI Books</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.tandfebooks.com/\"><strong>Taylor &amp; francis ebooks</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://archive.org/details/texts?and%5B%5D=mediatype%3A%22texts%22\"><strong>Ebooks &amp; Text</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://e-journal.unair.ac.id/JFIKI\"><strong>JFIKI (jurnal farmasi dan ilmu kefarmasian Indonesia)</strong></a></li>