(12, 's1-pendidikan-bahasa-arab', 'S1 – Pendidikan Bahasa Arab', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Pendidikan Bahasa Arab.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>305</strong>&nbsp;: Sosial Linguistik</li><li><strong>306</strong>&nbsp;: Kebudayaan</li><li><strong>398</strong>&nbsp;: Floklore</li><li><strong>410</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;: Linguistik Umum</li><li><strong>415</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;: Grammar</li><li><strong>499</strong>&nbsp;: Language</li><li><strong>808</strong>&nbsp;: Puisi</li><li><strong>899</strong>&nbsp;: Melayu Literature</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Pendidikan Bahasa Arab, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><p>1.&nbsp; Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Internasional, hampir semua jurnal berikut terindeks oleh Scopus:</p><ul><li><a href=\"http://ijllnet.com/index.php/archive\"><strong>International Journal of Language and Linguistics</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://ijlcnet.com/archive-ijlc\"><strong>International Journal of Linguistics and Communication</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://www.lancaster.ac.uk/jais/volume/index.htm\"><strong>Journal of Arabic and Islamic Studies</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://ccis2k.org/iajit/?option=com_content&amp;task=blogcategory&amp;id=112&amp;Itemid=399\"><strong>The International Arab Journal of Information Technology (IAJIT)</strong></a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;2.&nbsp;Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Nasional:</p><ul><li><a href=\"http://ejournal.uin-suka.ac.id/adab/Adabiyyat/issue/archive\"><strong>Adabiyyat</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://jurnal.uin-antasari.ac.id/index.php/al-banjari/issue/view/195\"><strong>Al-Banjari : Jurnal Ilmiah Ilmu-Ilmu Keislaman</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://jurnal.fib.uns.ac.id/index.php/al-buhuts/issue/archive\"><strong>Al-Buhuts</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://jurnal.uin-antasari.ac.id/index.php/alhadharah/issue/archive\"><strong>Alhadharah</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://journal.imla.or.id/index.php/arabi/issue/archive\"><strong>Arabi: Journal of Arabic Studies</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://jurnal.uin-antasari.ac.id/index.php/taradhi/issue/archive\"><strong>At-Taradhi</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://journal.uinjkt.ac.id/index.php/al-turats/issue/archive\"><strong>Buletin Al-Turas</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://jurnal.uin-antasari.ac.id/index.php/ittihad/issue/archive\"><strong>Ittihad</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://jurnal.uin-antasari.ac.id/index.php/maqoyis/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Al Maqoyis</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://ejournal.uin-suka.ac.id/tarbiyah/almahara\"><strong>Jurnal AL-MAHARA</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://jurnal.uin-antasari.ac.id/index.php/ushuluddin/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Ilmiah Ilmu Ushuluddin</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.unhas.ac.id/arab/journal.php?db9e66080bba8c99f6407b1a2e7a87c4a151e699b9135c0b84aab7bdcd67ce51\"><strong>Jurnal Nady Al-Adab</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnal.ugm.ac.id/poetika/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Poetika</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://jurnal.uin-antasari.ac.id/index.php/insania/issue/view/304\"><strong>Jurnal Studia Insania</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://jurnal.uin-antasari.ac.id/index.php/talim/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Ta’lim</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://jurnal.uin-antasari.ac.id/index.ph