(14, 's1-arsitektur', 'S1 – Arsitektur', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Arsitektur.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>720</strong> : Arsitektur</li><li><strong>720.1</strong> : Filsafat dan Teori Arsitektur</li><li><strong>726</strong> : Arsitektur Bangunan Keagamaan</li><li><strong>720.1</strong> : Filsafat dan Teori Arsitektur</li><li><strong>729</strong> : Desain dan Pola Bangunan</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Arsitektur, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.bookrix.com/books;architecture,id:2.html\"><strong>BookRix</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://http//www.e-booksdirectory.com/listing.php?category=336\"><strong>E-Books Directory</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://http//www.freebookcentre.net/CompuScience/Free-Computer-Architecture-Books-Download.html\"><strong>FreeBookCente.net</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.archnet-ijar.net/\"><strong>ArchNet International Journal of Architectural Research</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/frontiers-of-architectural-research\"><strong>Frontiers of architectural research</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://academic.oup.com/ijlct/search-results?page=1&amp;q=architecture&amp;fl_SiteID=5174&amp;allJournals=1&amp;SearchSourceType=1\"><strong>International Journal of Low Carbon Technologies</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://doaj.org/\"><strong>Spatium&nbsp;</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://doaj.org/toc/\"><strong>Iteraction design and architectur</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.revistas.uchile.cl/index.php/INVI\"><strong>Revista Invi</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/architecture\"><strong>Footprint</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.arcc-journal.org/index.php/arccjournal/issue/archive\"><strong>Enquiry&nbsp;</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.omicsonline.org/searchresult.php?keyword=architecture&amp;search=\"><strong>OMIC</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.elsevier.com/search-results?query=govrnment+administration&amp;labels=journals\"><strong>Elsevier</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.fupress.net/index.php/techne/issue/view/1351\"><strong>Techn&nbsp;</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.jacces.org/index.php/jacces/issue/archive\"><strong>Journal of Accessibility and Design for All</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://arsitektur.ub.ac.id/\"><strong>Jurnal Universitas Brawijaya</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://id.portalgaruda.org/?ref=browse&amp;mod=viewjournal&amp;journal=346&amp;action=search&amp;tsearch=architecture&amp;button=search+title+inside+journal\"><strong>Ipi</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Encyclopedias</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.britannica.com/topic/architecture\"><strong>Encyclopedia britannica</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780195300826.001.0001/acref-9780195300826\"><strong>Oxford reference</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/architecture/\"><strong>Stanford encyclopedia of philosophy</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://books.google.co.id/books?id=opvy1zGI2EcC&amp;pg=PA257&amp;lpg=PA257&amp;dq=encyclopedia+for+architecture&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=PPNXtb10nz&amp;sig=EcMFwBmqy2VYTbhhF8qxJGQ6tqc&amp;hl=id&amp;sa=X&amp;redir_esc=y#v=onepage&amp;q=encyclopedia%20for%20architecture&amp;f=false\"><strong>Encyclopedia of 20th century architecture</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Dictionaries</st