hanical%20engineering\"><strong>Accounting Tools</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://dictionary.cambridge.org/dictionary/english/mechanical-engineering\"><strong>Cambrige Dictionary</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/mechanical%20engineering\"><strong>Reviso</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://accountingstudy.com/accounting-courses/financial-accounting-terms-dictionary/accounting-terms-dictionary-definitions.htm\"><strong>Financial Accounting Terms Dictionary</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/english/accountancy\"><strong>Collins</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Scholarships</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.nsacct.org/about/nsa-scholarship-foundation\"><strong>NSA ( Nationals Society of accountants)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.gfoa.org/scholarships\"><strong>Government&nbsp; finance Officers Association</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.gocollege.com/financial-aid/scholarships/career/mechanical-engineer-scholarships.html\"><strong>Scholarships.com</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.aicpa.org/BecomeACPA/Scholarships/Pages/default.aspx\"><strong>AICPA</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.otago.ac.nz/accountancyfinance/study/scholarships/otago0149561.html\"><strong>Accountancy &amp; finance</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.amarilloareafoundation.org/_redesign-2013/pages/internal/receive---scholarship-bush-copy\"><strong>Amarilloareafoundation</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.pstap.org/member-benefits/student-scholarships/\"><strong>Pennsylvania society of tax &amp; accounting profesionals</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://scholarship-positions.com/research-school-accounting-indonesia-university-partner-scholarship-australia/2017/10/05/\"><strong>Scholarship positions</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Awards</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.usf.edu/research-innovation/sr/pa/award-accounting.aspx\">