ive\"><strong>Jurnal Psikologi Indonesia, UIN Sunan Ampel</strong></a><a href=\"http://ejournal.uksw.edu/refleksihukum\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Encyclopedias</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://psychcentral.com/encyclopedia/\"><strong>PsychCentral</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://psychology.oxfordre.com/\"><strong>Oxford Research Encyclopedias</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.britannica.com/\"><strong>Encyclopedia Brittanica</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Dictionaries</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/psychology\"><strong>The Free Dictionary by Farlex</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://www.dictionary.com/browse\"><strong>Dictionary.com</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://dictionary.cambridge.org/\"><strong>Cambridge Dictionary</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.merriam-webster.com/\"><strong>Merriam-Webster Dictionary</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Scholarships</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.psychology.org/scholarships/\"><strong>Physcology Scholarship</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.unigo.com/scholarships/by-major/psychology-scholarships\"><strong>Psychology Scholarships</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.scholarships.com/financial-aid/college-scholarships/scholarships-by-major/psychology-scholarships/\"><strong>Scholarship.com</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://www.apa.org/about/awards/\"><strong>APA</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.topuniversities.com/student-info/scholarship-advice/psychology-scholarships-around-world\"><strong>Psychology Scholarships Around the World</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Awards</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.div12.org/awards/\"><strong>Society of clinical psychology</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.apa.org/science/awards/\"><strong>American Psychology&nbsp; Association</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.psychology.org.au/about/awards/\"><strong>Australian Psychology Society</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.bestcounselingdegrees.net/lists/5-prestigious-awards-in-the-field-of-psychology/\"><strong>Best Counselling Degrees</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://grawemeyer.org/psychology/\"><strong>Grawemeyer Awards</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.psychologicalscience.org/members/awards-and-honors\"><strong>APS Association for Physicological Science</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.isixsigma.com/community/blogs/psychology-awards/\"><strong>SixSigma</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.siue.edu/education/psychology/newsletter.shtml\"><strong>Southern&nbsp; Illinous University Edwardsville</strong></a></li></ul>', '2024-12-18 06:43:33', '2025-12-06 15:05:08'),
(17, 's1-kebidanan', 'S1 – Kebidanan', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam Ilmu Kebidanan.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>612</strong> : Fisiologi Manusia, Ilmu Faal, Anatomi dan Fisiologi Manusia</li><li><strong>613</strong> : Kesehatan dan Keamanan Pribadi</li><li><strong>616</strong> : Penyakit</li><li><strong>617</strong> : Bedah dan pembedahan, pengobatan bagian</li><li><strong>618</strong> : Ginekologi, Obstetrik, Pediatrik, Geriatrik</li><li><strong>618.01</strong> : Filsafat dan Teori Ginekologi, Obstetrik, Pediatrik, Geriatrik</li><li><strong>618.14</strong> : Penyakit pada Rahim dan Mulut Rahim</li><li><strong>618.145</strong> : Bedah pada Rahim</li><li><strong>618.18</strong> : Pengaturan Kelahiran</li><li><strong>618.2</strong> : Obstetrik, Ilmu Kebidanan</li><li><strong>618.24</strong> : Keperawatan Pra Melahirkan dan Persiapan Melahirkan</li><li><strong>618.25</strong> : Kehamilan dan Kelahiran Kembar</li><li><strong>618.31</strong> : Kehamilan di Luar Kandungan</li><li><strong>618.39</strong> : Keguguran dan Kelahiran Prematur</li><li><strong>618.4</strong> : Persalinan</li><li><strong>618.5</strong> : Permasalahan dalam Persalinan</li><li><strong>618.6</strong> : Masa Setelah Melahirkan yang Berlangsung Normal</li><li><strong>618.8</strong> : Bedah Kebidanan</li><li><strong>618.86</strong> : Bedah Caesar</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Ilmu Kebidanan, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4>&nbsp;</h4><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.elsevier.com/\"><strong>Textbook for Midwives</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/\"><strong>Public Health</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.taylorfrancis.com/\"><strong>Obstetrics by Ten Teachers</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/midwifery\"><strong>Midwifery Journal</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://medicalxpress.com/journals/bmc-pregnancy-and-childbirth/\"><strong>BMC Pregnancy and Childbirth</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://reproductive-health-journal.biomedcentral.com/\"><strong>Reproductive Health Journal</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://obgyn.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/journal/18793479\"><strong>International Journal of Gynecology &amp; Obstetrics (IJGO)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.poltekkes-denpasar.ac.id/index.php/JIK/index\"><strong>Jurnal Ilmu Kebidanan (JIK)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://salnesia.id/jibi\"><strong>Jurnal Ilmu Kebidanan Dan Kesehatan</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.almaata.ac.id/index.php/JNKI/index\"><strong>Jurnal Ners dan Kebidanan Indonesia</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.e-journal.poltekkesjogja.ac.id/index.php/kia\"><strong>Jurnal Kesehatan Ibu dan Anak (Jurnal KIA)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://e-journal.ibi.or.id/index.php/jib\"><strong>Jurnal Bidan Indonesia (JBI)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://sinta.kemdikbud.go.id/journals/profile/91#!\"><strong>Jurnal Kebidanan dan Keperawatan \'Aisyiyah</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ijnms.net/index.php/ijnms/issue/view/24 \"><strong>International Journal of Nursing and Midwifery Science</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://nmsjournal.kaums.ac.ir/\"><strong>Nursing and Midwifery Studies</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejurnalstikeskesdamudayana.ac.id/index.php/wuj\"><strong>Jurnal Pengabdian kepada Masyarakat Wahana Usada (WUJ)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.poltekkes-smg.ac.id/ojs/index.php/jurkeb/index\"><strong>Jurnal Kebidanan (JKB)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://e-journal.unair.ac.id/MOG\"><strong>Majalah Obstetri &amp; Ginekologi (Journal of Obstetrics &amp; Gynecology Science)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.poltekkes-smg.ac.id/ojs/index.php/JSK/index\"><strong>Jurnal Sains Kebidanan</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.poltekharber.ac.id/index.php/siklus\"><strong>Journal Research Midwifery Politeknik Tegal</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnal.univrab.ac.id/index.php/jomis\"><strong>Journal of Midwifery Science (JOMIS)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnal.unimus.ac.id/index.php/jur_bid/\"><strong>Jurnal Kebidanan</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnal.poltekkespalu.ac.id/index.php/JBC/\"><strong>Jurnal Bidan Cerdas</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.almaata.ac.id/index.php/JNKI/index\"><strong>Jurnal Ners dan Kebidanan Indonesia</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.ummat.ac.id/index.php/MJ/index\"><strong>Midwifery Journal : Jurnal Kebidanan UM Mataram</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnal.unipasby.ac.id/index.php/embrio\"><strong>Embrio Jurnal Kebidanan Universitas PGRI Adi Buana Surabaya</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journaliakmitangsel2.iakmi.or.id/index.php/kespro/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Kespro</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/womens-health-issues\"><strong>Elsevier</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.dovepress.com/international-journal-of-womens-health-i1964-j45\"><strong>International Journal of Women\'s Healt</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/women-and-birth\"><strong>Women and Birth</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Encyclopedias</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.britannica.com/\"><strong>Encyclopedia Britannica</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://medlineplus.gov/\"><strong>MedlinePlus</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.ebsco.com/\"><strong>EBSCOhost</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.ncbi.