cholarship positions</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Awards</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.usf.edu/research-innovation/sr/pa/award-accounting.aspx\"><strong>USF Research &amp; innovation</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.internationalaccountingbulletin.com/News/2016-the-accountant-international-accounting-bulletin-awards-winners-5027238\"><strong>International Accounting Bulletin</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.bdo.com.do/en-gb/news/2016/wins-award-bdo-international-accounting-bulletin-(\"><strong>BDO</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.rsm.global/news/rsm-scoops-editor%E2%80%99s-special-award-international-accounting-bulletin-awards\"><strong>RSM</strong></a></li><li><strong>&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"http://www.kreston.im/2012/03/kreston-network-wins-international-accounting-bulletin-award/\"><strong>Kreston</strong></a></li><li><strong>&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://www.accountantsdaily.com.au/australian-accounting-awards/winners/2017-winners\"><strong>Accountantsdaily Australian Accounting Award 2017</strong></a></li><li><strong>&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"http://www.nsacct.org/nsacctwww/education-events/nsa-annual-awards\"><strong>NSA National Society Of Accountants</strong></a></li><li><strong>&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://www.cpacanada.ca/en/connecting-and-news/awards\"><strong>CPA Chartered Professional&nbsp; Accountants Canada</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;</a>&nbsp;</li></ul>', '2025-01-06 05:50:58', '2025-12-07 07:33:55'),
(24, 's1-pendidikan-agama-islam', 'S1 – Pendidikan Agama Islam', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Pendidikan Agama Islam.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>2X7</strong> Filsafat dan Perkembangan Islam</li><li><strong>2X7.1</strong> Filsafat Islam&nbsp;</li><li><strong>2X7.15 </strong>Psikologi Islam</li><li><strong>2X7.3&nbsp;</strong>Pendidikan Islam, Sekolah Islam</li><li><strong>2X7.341 </strong>Pondok Pesantren</li><li><strong>371.077 </strong>Islamic Schools/Sekolah Islam</li><li><strong>372.84 </strong>Religion for Primary Education/Pelajaran Agama untuk Pendidikan Dasar</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Pendidikan Agama Islam, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><p>1.&nbsp; Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Internasional, hampir semua jurnal berikut terindeks oleh Scopus:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://ajis.org/index.php/ajiss\"><strong>American Journal of Islam and Society</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://moraref.kemenag.go.id/archives/journal/98077985952795871\"><strong>IJISH</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.uinsi.ac.id/index.php/syamil/index\"><strong>SYAMIL</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.umy.ac.id/index.php/ijiep\"><strong>IJIEP</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://attarbiyah.iainsalatiga.ac.id/index.php/attarbiyah/\"><strong>ATTARBIYAH</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.uin-malang.ac.id/index.php/jpai\"><strong>J-PAI</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.umpo.ac.id/index.php/istawa/index\"><strong>Istawa</strong></a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;2.&nbsp;Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Nasional:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://journal.uhamka.ac.id/jpi\"><strong>Jurnal Pendidikan Islam</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.ejournal.staindirundeng.ac.id/index.php/tadib\"><strong>At-Ta\'dib</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.tarbiya.org/\"><strong>TARBIYA</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnaledukasia.org/index.php/edukasia\"><strong>Edukasia</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.neliti.com/journals/al-idarah\"><strong>Al-Idarah</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://books.google.com/\"><strong>BookGoogle.com</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://iou.edu.gm/\"><strong>Islamic Online University</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/\"><strong>ResearchGate</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.scribd.com/\"><strong>Scribd</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Encyclopedias</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://referenceworks.brill.com/display/package/eio\"><strong>Encyclopaedia of Islam (EI)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780195300826.001.0001/acref-9780195300826\"><strong>Oxford reference</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://muslimheritage.com/\"><strong>Muslim Heritage</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.britannica.com/\"><strong>Encyclopaedia Britannica</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Dictionaries</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://corpus.quran.com/\"><strong>Qur’anic Arabic Corpus</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://shamela.ws/\"><strong>Shamela Library</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.wordreference.com/\"><strong>WordReference Arabic-English Dictionary</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Scholarships</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.turkiyeburslari.gov.tr/\"><strong>Turkey Scholarships</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.chevening.org/\"><strong>Chevening Scholarship</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.qf.org.qa/\"><strong>Qatar Foundation Scholarships</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Awards</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://kingfaisalprize.org/\"><strong>King Faisal International Prize</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.ha.ae/\"><strong>Sheikh Hamdan Bin Rashid Al Maktoum</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://gifaawards.com/home\"><strong>Global Islamic Finance Awards (GIFA)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://icesco.org/en/\"><strong>ISESCO Prize for Education and Science</strong></a></li></ul>', '2025-01-06 05:57:26', '2025-12-06 15:47:39'),
(25, 's1-bimbingan-dan-penyuluhan-islam', 'S1 – Bimbingan dan Penyuluhan Islam', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Bimbingan dan Penyuhan Islam.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>200</strong> : Agama</li><li>2X0 : Islam Umum</li><li><strong>2x1</strong> : Islam</li><li>2X3 : Akidah &amp; Akhlak</li><li>2X7 : Pendidikan &amp; Penyuluhan</li><li>2X7.1 : Konseling Islam</li><li>2X7.2 : Psikologi Islam</li><li>2X7.3 : Bimbingan Keluarga</li><li>2X8 : Dakwah</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Bimbingan dan Penyuhan Islam, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><p>1.&nbsp; Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Internasional, hampir semua jurnal berikut terindeks oleh Scopus:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://igcjournal.com/index.php/submissionportal\"><strong>IGCJournal</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jicc.umy.ac.id/index.php/jicc\"><strong>JICC</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/\"><strong>PubMed</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ojs.attanwir.ac.id/index.php/jbki\"><strong>Al-Ihath</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.tandfonline.com/\"><strong>Taylor &amp; Francis Online</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.uinjkt.ac.id/\"><strong>Al-Qalam Journal</strong></a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;2.&nbsp;Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Nasional:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://md.walisongo.ac.id/jurnal-jid/\"><strong>Jurnal-jidJurnal Ilmu Dakwah</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://sinta.kemdikbud.go.id/journals/profile/3529#!\"><strong>Jurnal bimbingan Konseling Indonesia</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://sinta.kemdikbud.go.id/journals/profile/12193#!\"><strong>Jurnal Ilmiah Bimbingan Konseling Undiksha