(27, 's1-teknologi-hasil-perikanan', 'S1 – Teknologi Hasil Perikanan', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Teknologi Hasil Perikanan.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>600</strong> : Teknologi, Ilmu Terapan</li><li><strong>630</strong> : Pertanian</li><li><strong>639</strong> : Perikanan, Peternakan, dan Subjek Terkait</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Teknologi Hasil Perikanan, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><p>1.&nbsp; Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Internasional, hampir semua jurnal berikut terindeks oleh Scopus:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://journals.sagepub.com/home/fst\"><strong>Food Science and Technology International (FSTI)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://link.springer.com/journal/13197\"><strong>Journal of Food Science and Technology (JFST)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://link.springer.com/journal/10499\"><strong>Aquaculture International</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.tandfonline.com/toc/wafp20/current\"><strong>Journal of Aquatic Food Product Technology (JAFPT)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/lwt\"><strong>LWT - Food Science and Technology</strong></a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;2.&nbsp;Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Nasional:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://journal.ipb.ac.id/index.php/jphpi/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Pengolahan Hasil Perikanan Indonesia (JPHPI)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.ipb.ac.id/index.php/jphpi/about\"><strong>Jurnal IPB</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.ipb.ac.id/index.php/jurnalikt/%22\"><strong>Jurnal Ilmu dan Teknologi Kelautan Tropis (JITKT)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ojs.unida.ac.id/jmss\"><strong>JURNAL MINA SAINS</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://kkp.go.id/\"><strong>Pengolahan Hasil Perikanan Tradisional</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/\"><strong>Postharvest Technology of Fish and Fish Products</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.wiley.com/en-sg\"><strong>Fish Processing: Sustainability and New Opportunities</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Encyclopedias</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.britannica.com/\"><strong>Britannica</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.elsevier.com/\"><strong>Encyclopedia of Fish Physiology</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://link.springer.com/\"><strong>SpringerLink</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/\"><strong>ScienceDirect</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Dictionaries</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.merriam-webster.com/\"><strong>Merriam-Webste &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.oxfordreference.com/\"><strong>Oxford Reference</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://books.google.com/\"><strong>Google Books</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Scholarships</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://foreign.fulbrightonline.org/\"><strong>Fulbright Scholarship (Amerika Serikat)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://foreign.fulbrightonline.org/\"><strong>Japan International Cooperation Agency (JICA)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://beasiswaunggulan.kemdikbud.go.id/\"><strong>Beasiswa Unggulan Kemendikbud</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://kkp.go.id/\"><strong>Beasiswa KKP (Kementerian Kelautan dan Perikanan)</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Awards</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.seafoodexpo.com/global/\"><strong>Seafood Excellence Global Awards</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.was.org/\"><strong>World Aquaculture Society (WAS)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.fao.org/home/en/\"><strong>FAO World Fisheries Award</strong></a></li></ul>', '2025-01-11 07:07:10', '2025-12-06 14:37:31'),
(28, 's1-pendidikan-islam-anak-usia-dini', 'S1 – Pendidikan Islam Anak Usia Dini', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Pendidikan Anak Usia Dini.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>370 - 379</strong> : Pendidikan</li><li><strong>371 &nbsp;</strong>: Pendidikan, Sekolah dan Aktifitasnya</li><li><strong>372.21</strong> : Pendidikan anak usia dini / PAUD&nbsp;</li><li><strong>372.218</strong> : Taman kanak-kanak</li><li><strong>373</strong> : Pendidikan Menengah</li><li><strong>375</strong> : Kurikulum</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Pendidikan Anak Usia Dini, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><p>1.&nbsp; Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Internasional, hampir semua jurnal berikut terindeks oleh Scopus:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/early-childhood-research-quarterly\"><strong>Early Childhood Research Quarterly (ECRQ)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://link.springer.com/journal/10643\"><strong>Early Childhood Education Journal</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://search.yahoo.com/search?fr=mcafee&amp;type=E210US91215G0&amp;p=Journal+of+Early+Childhood+Research\"><strong>Journal of Early Childhood Research</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.tandfonline.com/journals/ciey20\"><strong>International Journal of Early Years Education</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://srcd.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/journal/14678624\"><strong>Child Development</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal2.um.ac.id/index.php/jpp/index\"><strong>Jurnal Pendidikan dan Pembelajaran</strong></a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;2.&nbsp;Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Nasional:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://unnes.ac.id/pendidikan-guru-paud-s1/\"><strong>Jurnal Pendidikan Anak Usia Dini (JPAUD)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://kjpupi.id/\"><strong>Jurnal Pendidikan Anak Usia Dini Indonesia (JPAUDI)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://sinta.kemdikbud.go.id/journals/profile/10372\"><strong>KIDDO: Jurnal pendidikan Islam Anak Usia Dini</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.stai-alittihad.ac.id/index.php/jurnalpiaud\"><strong>Al-ittihad</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://bookboon.com/\"><strong>BookBoon</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://books.google.com/\"><strong>BookGoogle.com</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.jstor.org/\"><strong>JSTOR</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://belajar.kemdikbud.go.id/\"><strong>Rumah Belajar</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Encyclopedias</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.cambridge.org/\"><strong>Cambridge</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pendidikan_anak_usia_dini\"><strong>Wikipedia</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.elsevier.com/\"><strong>Elsevier</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.britannica.com/\"><strong>Encyclopaedia Britannica</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Dictionaries</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.oxfordreference.com/\"><strong>Oxford Dictionary of Education</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.cambridge.org/core/books/cambridge-dictionary-of-sociology/EAA9DFF124770B2C7DACD299F2AC7353\"><strong>The Cambridge Dictionary of Sociology</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.merriam-webster.com/\"><strong>The Merriam-Webster Dictionary</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Scholarships</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.chevening.org/\"><strong>Chevening Scholarship</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.id.emb-japan.go.jp/itpr_id/sch.html\"><strong>beasiswa MEXT</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Awards</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://melbourne-cshe.unimelb.edu.au/awards/university-of-melbourne-awards-for-excellence\"><strong>The International Excellence Award (University of Melbourne)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://globalteacherprize.org/\"><strong>The Global Teacher Prize</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.wisecampaign.org.uk/wise-awards-2025/\"><strong>The WISE Awards</strong></a></li></ul>', '2025-01-11 07:41:02', '2025-12-06 15:58:13'),
(29, 's1-ilmu-al-quran-dan-tafsir', 'S1 – Ilmu Al-Quran dan Tafsir', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Ilmu Al-Qur\'an dan Tafsir.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>2X0&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Islam</strong></li><li><strong>2X1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Al-Qur’an</strong></li><li><strong>2X1.1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Ulumul Qur’an</strong></li><li><strong>2X1.2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Sejarah Al-Qur’an</strong></li><li><strong>2X1.3&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Tafsir Klasik</strong></li><li><strong>2X1.4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Aplikasi Tafsir&nbsp;</strong></li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Ilmu Al-Qur\'an dan Tafsir, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><p>1.&nbsp; Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Internasional, hampir semua jurnal berikut terindeks oleh Scopus:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://journals2.ums.ac.id/index.php/qist?utm_source\"><strong>QiST: Journal of Quran and Tafseer Studies</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.uinsgd.ac.id/index.php/mashadiruna?utm_source\"><strong>Mashadiruna: Jurnal Ilmu Al-Qur\'an dan Tafsir</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.uit-lirboyo.ac.id/index.php/alkarim?utm_source\"><strong>Al-Karim: International Journal of Quranic and Islamic Studies</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.jurnalalmunir.com/index.php/al-munir\"><strong>Al-Munir: Jurnal Studi Ilmu Al-Qur\'an dan Tafsir</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.nurulqadim.ac.id/index.php/jtit\"><strong>Al-Qadim: Jurnal Tafsir dan Ilmu Tafsir</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.uinjkt.ac.id/index.php/journal-of-quran-and-hadith?utm_source\"><strong>Journal of Qur\'an and Hadith Studies</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejurnal.iiq.ac.id/index.php/El-Maeda?utm_source\"><strong>El-Maeda: Jurnal Al-Quran dan Tafsir</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.iai-tabah.ac.id/index.php/Alfurqon/peer?utm_source\"><strong>Al Furqan: Jurnal Ilmu Al Quran dan Tafsir</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnalfuda.iainkediri.ac.id/index.php/qof?utm_source\"><strong>QOF: Jurnal Studi Al-Qur\'an dan Tafsir</strong></a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;2.&nbsp;Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Nasional:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://jurnal.asy-syukriyyah.ac.id/index.php/JIQTA\"><strong>Jurnal Ilmu Al-Qur\'an dan Tafsir (JIQTA)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.iai-tabah.ac.id/index.php/Alfurqon/peer?utm_source\"><strong>Al Furqan: Jurnal Ilmu Al Quran dan Tafsir</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://moraref.kemenag.go.id/archives/journal/25426173609641527\"><strong>Al-Bayan: Jurnal Studi Al-Qur\'an dan Tafsir</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.iainlangsa.ac.id/index.php/tibyan\"><strong>Jurnal At-Tibyan: Jurnal Ilmu Alqur\'an dan Tafsir</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.uinsgd.ac.id/index.php/mashadiruna?utm_source\"><strong>Mashadiruna: Jurnal Ilmu Al-Qur\'an dan Tafsir</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnalfuda.iainkediri.ac.id/index.php/qof?utm_source\"><strong>QOF: Jurnal Studi Al-Qur\'an dan Tafsir</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejurnal.iiq.ac.id/index.php/alfanar\"><strong>Al-Fanar: Jurnal Ilmu Al-Qur\'an dan Tafsir</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.iaifa.ac.id/index.php/takwiluna/index\"><strong>Ta\'wiluna: Jurnal Ilmu Al-Qur\'an, Tafsir dan Pemikiran Islam</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnal.staialhidayahbogor.ac.id/index.php/alt\"><strong>Al-Tadabbur: Jurnal Ilmu Al-Qur\'an dan Tafsir</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://alquran-sunnah.com/artikel/buku-islam/ebook-islami/454-e-book-tafsir-ibnu-katsir-salah-satu-kitab-tafsir-al-quran-terbaik.html\"><strong>E-Books Tafsir Al-Qur\'an</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.academia.edu/55141347/Pengantar_Studi_Ilmu_Al_Quran_by_Syaikh_Manna_Al_Qaththan_z_lib_org_\"><strong>academia.edu</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://archive.org/details/pengantar-ulumul-quran/page/42/mode/2up\"><strong>Pengantar Ilmu Al-Quran</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.kalamullah.com/Books/Tafsir%20Ibn%20Kathir%20all%2010%20volumes.pdf\"><strong>Tafsir Ibnu Katsir</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ebooksunnah.com/en/ebooks?category=al-quran-al-karim&amp;page=2&amp;sort=relevance&amp;viewMode=list&amp;yfwIiz=AYmcAQ\"><strong>E-books Islami Ahlus Sunnah wal Jama\'ah</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://archive.org/details/kumpulan-kitab-buku-tafsir/Ahsan%20al-had%C3%AEts%20analisis%20tekstual%20ulumul%20quran/\"><strong>Tafsir Al-Qur\'an</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Encyclopedias</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://referenceworks.brill.com/display/db/eqo\"><strong>Encyclopaedia of the Qur\'ān</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://iequran.com/\"><strong>Integrated Encyclopedia of the Qur\'an (IEQ)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Quran-Encyclopedia-Oliver-Leaman/dp/0415775299\"><strong>The Qur\'an: An Encyclopedia</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Dictionaries</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://books.google.co.id/books/about/Kamus_Al_Qur_an_Quranic_Explorer.html?id=CjGTCwAAQBAJ&amp;redir_esc=y\"><strong>Kamus Al-Qur\'an: Quranic Explorer</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://lajnah.kemenag.go.id/berita/penyusunan-kamus-kosakata-al-qur-an\"><strong>Penyusunan Kamus Kosakata Al-Qur\'an</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://openlibrary.org/books/OL3775635M/Kamus_istilah_agama_Islam_(KIAI)\"><strong>Kamus Istilah Agama Islam (KIAI)</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Scholarships</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://iiq.ac.id/berita/beasiswa-pbsb-2024/?utm_source\"><strong>Beasiswa Santri Berprestasi (PBSB) di Institut Ilmu Al-Qur’an (IIQ) Jakarta</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://lpdp.kemenkeu.go.id/en/beasiswa/targeted/beasiswa-pendidikan-kader-ulama-2025?utm_source\"><strong>Beasiswa Pendidikan Kader Ulama (PKU) oleh LPDP</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://pmb.idaqu.ac.id/1000beasiswa?utm_source\"><strong>Program 1000 Beasiswa untuk Indonesia oleh Institut Daarul Qur\'an (Idaqu)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://s2iat.walisongo.ac.id/index.php/2024/05/03/program-magister-s2-ilmu-al-quran-dan-tafsir-uin-walisongo-semarang-membuka-pendaftaran-mahasiswa-baru-tahun-akademik-2024-2025/?utm_source\"><strong>Beasiswa Tahfidz 30 Juz di UIN Walisongo Semarang</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://stiqarrahman.ac.id/?utm_source\"><strong>Beasiswa KIP Kuliah Kemenag di STIQ Ar-Rahman</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Awards</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://nu.or.id/nasional/jqhnu-berikan-anugerah-penghargaan-kepada-tokoh-dan-lembaga-pendidikan-al-quran-KLpfC?utm_source=chatgpt.com\"><strong>Penghargaan kepada Tokoh dan Lembaga Pendidikan Al-Qur\'an oleh JQHNU</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://fuh.uin-antasari.ac.id/alumni-ilmu-al-quran-dan-tafsir-uin-antasari-raih-juara-iii-karya-tulis-ilmiah-pada-mtq-nasional-ke-30/?utm_source\"><strong>Prestasi Mahasiswa dalam Lomba Karya Tulis Ilmiah Al-Qur\'an</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://iiq.ac.id/berita/iiq-jakarta-raih-penghargaan-bergengsi-di-multaqo-nasional-ulama-quran-jqh-nu/?utm_source\"><strong>Penghargaan dalam Multaqo Nasional Ulama Qur\'an JQH NU</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://iqt.iain-palangkaraya.ac.id/2024/07/10/prestasi-gemilang-di-ajang-musabaqah-tilawatil-quran-mtq-ke-55-mahasiswa-ilmu-al-quran-dan-tafsir-borong-penghargaan-bergengsi-dan-harumkan-nama-kampus/?utm_source\"><strong>Prestasi Mahasiswa dalam Musabaqah Tilawatil Qur\'an (MTQ) ke-55</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://idaqu.ac.id/mila-kamilah-mahasiswa-idaqu-raih-sanad-al-quran-30-juz/?utm_source\"><strong>Penerimaan Sanad Al-Qur\'an 30 Juz</strong></a></li></ul>', '2025-01-22 07:26:33', '2025-12-07 07:14:34');
INSERT INTO `resources` (`id`, `slug`, `prodi`, `resource`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(30, 's3-studi-islam', 'S3 – Studi Islam', '<h3><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h3><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Ilmu Studi Islam.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>2X0 </strong>Islam&nbsp;: Filsafat, Ilmu Sosial, Bahasa, Ilmu Murni, Ilmu Terapan, Teknologi, Kesenian&nbsp;</li><li><strong>2X1 </strong>Al-Qur\'an (Al Qur\'an, Alquran, Quran) dan Ilmu yang Berkaitan&nbsp;</li><li><strong>2X2 </strong>Al-Hadits dan yang Berkaitan&nbsp;</li><li><strong>2X3 </strong>Aqidah, Ilmu Kalam&nbsp;</li><li><strong>2X4 </strong>Fikih, Fiqih, Fiqh, Hukum Islam&nbsp;</li><li><strong>2X5 </strong>Akhlak/Tasawuf</li><li><strong>2X6 </strong>Sosial dan Budaya Islam&nbsp;</li><li><strong>2X7 </strong>Filsafat dan Perkembangan Islam</li><li><strong>2X8 </strong>Aliran dan Sekte dalam Islam&nbsp;</li><li><strong>2X9 </strong>Sejarah Islam&nbsp;</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Untuk mengetahui buku Studi Islam, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h3><ul><li><a href=\"https://sites.google.com/ibrahimy.ac.id/koleksiperpusibrahimy/halaman-muka/e-book\">E-book&nbsp;</a></li><li><a href=\"https://sites.google.com/ibrahimy.ac.id/koleksiperpusibrahimy/halaman-muka/monograph?authuser=0\">E-monograph</a></li><li><a href=\"https://muslim.or.id/category/akidah\">muslim.or.id</a></li><li><a href=\"https://ebooksunnah.com/en\">ebooksunnah.com</a></li><li><a href=\"https://ilmuislam.id/ebook\">ilmuislam.id</a></li><li><a href=\"https://elibrary.stebisigm.ac.id/index.php?p=e-book\">stebisigm.ac.id</a></li><li><a href=\"https://artikel.alfurqongresik.com/ebook-islami/\">Media Dakwah Ma’had Al-Furqon</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.alquran-sunnah.com/artikel/buku-islam/ebook-islami.html\">Al-Qur\'an dan Sunnah</a></li><li><a href=\"https://archive.org/details/KumpulannBUKUParaULAMA/AbdulAzizBinMuhammadAs-sadhan-SorotanTotalUlamaSalaf/\">Internet Archive</a></li><li><a href=\"https://islamicbulletin.org/\">islamicbulletin.org</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.allahsword.com/free_islamic_books.html\">allahsword.com</a></li><li><a href=\"https://yaqeeninstitute.org/read/books\">yaqeeninstitute.org</a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h3><ul><li><a href=\"https://academic.oup.com/jis\">Journal of Islamic Studies Oxford University</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.aljamiah.or.id/ajis/about\">Al-Jami\'ah: Journal of Islamic Studies</a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnal.uin-antasari.ac.id/index.php/khazanah\">Khazanah: Jurnal Studi Islam dan Humaniora</a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.umy.ac.id/index.php/afkaruna\">Afkaruna: Indonesian Interdisciplinary Journal of Islamic Studies</a></li><li><a href=\"https://e-journal.uingusdur.ac.id/index.php/hikmatuna\">HIKMATUNA: Journal for Integrative Islamic Studies</a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.uinsaid.ac.id/index.php/dinika\">Dinika Academic Journal of Islamic Studies</a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.unj.ac.id/unj/index.php/hayula\">Hayula: Indonesian Journal of Multidisciplinary Islamic Studies</a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.iaincurup.ac.id/index.php/AJIS\">AJIS : Academic Journal of Islamic Studies</a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal2.uad.ac.id/index.php/almisbah\">AL-MISBAH (Jurnal Islamic Studies)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal2.uad.ac.id/index.php/ijish\">IJISH (International Journal of Islamic Studies and Humanities)&nbsp;</a></li><li><a href=\"https://millati.iainsalatiga.ac.id/index.php/millati/index\">MILLATI: Journal of Islamic Studies and Humanities</a></li><li><a href=\"https://insight.ppj.unp.ac.id/index.php/insight\">International Journal of Islamic Studies Higher Education</a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.uinsi.ac.id/index.php/bijis\">Borneo International Journal of Islamic Studies</a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.alhikmahjkt.ac.id/index.php/HIKMAH\">Hikmah : Journal of Islamic Studies</a></li><li><a href=\"https://al-afkar.com/index.php/Afkar_Journal\">al-Afkar, Journal For Islamic Studies</a></li><li><a href=\"https://journals.researchsynergypress.com/index.php/ijeiis\">International Journal of Emerging Issues in Islamic Studies</a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.kopertais4.or.id/madura/index.php/alirfani\">Al-Irfan: Journal of Arabic Literature and Islamic Studies</a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.walisongo.ac.id/index.php/wahana/index\">Wahana Akademika: Jurnal Studi Islam dan Sosial</a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnalnasional.ump.ac.id/index.php/Alhamra\">Alhamra Jurnal Studi Islam</a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnal.faiunwir.ac.id/index.php/Jurnal_Risalah\">Risalah, Jurnal Pendidikan dan Studi Islam</a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal2.uad.ac.id/index.php/insyirah\">Insyirah: Jurnal Ilmu Bahasa Arab dan Studi Islam</a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.iai-tabah.ac.id/index.php/madinah/issue/archive\">Madinah: Jurnal Studi Islam</a></li><li><a href=\"https://lisyabab.staimaswonogiri.ac.id/lisyabab\">Jurnal Studi Islam dan Sosial</a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.iaingorontalo.ac.id/index.php/aj/index\">Jurnal Ilmiah AL-Jauhari Jurnal Studi Islam dan Interdisipliner</a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnal.radenfatah.ac.id/index.php/medinate\">Medina-Te : Jurnal Studi Islam</a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.stismu.ac.id/ojs/index.php/qolamuna\">qolamuna : Jurnal studi islam</a></li><li><p><a href=\"https://jasika.umy.ac.id/index.php/jasika\">Jurnal Studi Islam dan Kemuhammadiyahan (JASIKA)</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p></li></ul><h3><i>Proceeding</i></h3><ul><li><a href=\"https://proceeding.uingusdur.ac.id/index.php/icis\">Proceeding of International Conference on Islamic Studies (ICIS)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnal.umsu.ac.id/index.php/insis\">Proceeding International Seminar of Islamic Studies (INSIS)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnal.uinsu.ac.id/index.php/ISCIS\">Proceeding International Seminar and Conference on Islamic Studies (ISCIS)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://proceedings.uin-alauddin.ac.id/index.php/icosis/\">International Conference on Science and Islamic Studies (ICOSIS)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://proceeding-fu.uinib.ac.id/index.php/aiconis\">Annual International Conference of Islamic Studies (AICONIS)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://proceeding.iainkudus.ac.id/index.php/PICCP\">Proceedings of the Postgraduate International Conference on Islamic Studies (PICIS)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://proceeding.uinmataram.ac.id/index.php/iconside\">Proceeding of International Conference on Islamic Education and Science Development (ICONSIDE)</a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><i>E-Dissertation</i></h3><ul><li><a href=\"https://digilib.uin-suka.ac.id/view/divisions/pps=5Fsi/\">Universitas Islam Negeri Sunan Kalijaga Yogyakarta</a></li><li><a href=\"https://repository.uinsa.ac.id/view/divisions/jur=5Fdsi/\">Universitas Islam Negeri Sunan Ampel Surabaya</a></li><li><a href=\"http://repo.uinsatu.ac.id/view/divisions/disertasi/\">Universitas Islam Negeri Sayyid Ali Rahmatullah Tulungagung</a></li><li><a href=\"http://repository.uin-malang.ac.id/view/divisions/doktor/\">Universitas Islam Negeri Maulana Malik Ibrahim Malang</a></li><li><a href=\"https://eprints.walisongo.ac.id/view/divisions/PPS76003/\">Universitas Islam Negeri Walisongo Semarang</a></li><li><a href=\"https://repository.uinjkt.ac.id/dspace/handle/123456789/171\">Universitas Islam Negeri Syarif Hidayatullah Jakarta</a></li><li><a href=\"https://repository.uinib.ac.id/view/divisions/sch=5Fdoktor/\">Universitas Islam Negeri Imam Bonjol Padang</a></li><li><a href=\"https://digilib.uinkhas.ac.id/view/divisions/s2=5Fsi/2024.html\">Universitas Islam Negeri KH. Ahmad Shiddiq Jember</a></li><li><p><a href=\"https://repository.uiii.ac.id/collections/ca5bdc3c-80f6-4674-a602-6f060e4cdb3f\">Universitas Islam Internasional Indonesia</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p></li></ul><h3><i><strong>Open Educational Resources (OER)</strong></i></h3><ul><li><a href=\"https://oercommons.org/search?search_source=site&amp;f.search=islam\">OER Commons</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.unesco.org/en/open-educational-resources\">UNESCO &nbsp;</a></li><li><a href=\"https://archive.org/details/education\">Archives library</a></li><li><a href=\"https://belajar.kemdikbud.go.id/\">Rumah Belajar Kementerian Pendidikan dan Kebudayaan RI</a></li><li><a href=\"https://libguides.unisa.ac.za/c.php?g=355602&amp;p=2398648\">University of South Africa</a></li><li><a href=\"https://podcasts.ox.ac.uk/open/all\">University of Oxford</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.monash.edu/library/services-for-teachers/open-educational-resources\">Monash University</a></li><li><a href=\"https://umlibguides.um.edu.my/oer\">Universiti Malaya</a></li><li><a href=\"https://weko.wou.edu.my/About-this-Repository/\">Wawasan Open University</a></li><li><a href=\"https://library.help.edu.my/open-education-resources-oer/\">HELP University</a></li><li><a href=\"https://pustaka.ut.ac.id/lib/oer/\">Universitas Terbuka</a></li><li><a href=\"https://oer.uinsyahada.ac.id/\">Universitas Islam Negeri Syekh Ali Hasan Ahmad Addary Padangsidimpuan</a></li><li><a href=\"https://uinsa.ac.id/oer\">Universitas Islam Negeri Sunan Ampel Surabaya</a></li><li><a href=\"https://oer.iainlhokseumawe.ac.id/index.php?callnumber=0&amp;search=search\">Institut Agama Islam Negeri Lhokweumawe</a></li></ul><h4>&nbsp;</h4><h3><i>Web of Knowledge</i></h3><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.sci-hub.se/\">SCI-HUB</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.scimagojr.com/\">Scimago Journal &amp; Country Rank</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/\">Semantic Scholar</a></li><li><a href=\"https://scispace.com/\">AI Chat for Scientific</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.ssrn.com/index.cfm/en/\">Social Science Research Network</a></li><li><a href=\"http://opencourselibrary.org/\">Open Course Library (OCL)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://spada.kemdikbud.go.id/\">SPADA : Sistem Pembelajaran Daring Indonesia</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.saylor.org/\">Saylor Academy</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.open.edu/openlearn/\">OpenLearn - The Open University</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.kaggle.com/learn\">Kaggle Course</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.merlot.org/merlot/index.htm\">MERLOT: Multimedia Educational Resource for Learning and Online Teaching.</a></li><li><a href=\"https://corpus.quran.com/\">Qur’anic Arabic Corpus</a></li><li><a href=\"https://shamela.ws/\">Shamela Library</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.wordreference.com/\">Word Reference Arabic-English Dictionary</a></li></ul><h4>&nbsp;</h4><h3><i><strong>Video</strong></i></h3><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCulDGImgrOq_X2T_mQJ8pyQ\">The Institute of Islamic Studies at the University of Toronto (IIS)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@oxfordcentreforislamicstudies\">Oxford Centre for Islamic Studies</a></li><li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/kr_oTzSxtb8\">Ngaji Filsafat 206 : Paulo Freire (Filsafat Pendidikan)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/gIYp2Oy4Q7E\">Psikologi pendidikan (Dr. H. Mamat Supriatna, M.Pd)&nbsp;</a></li><li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/A-VSvip_RdE\">Filsafat Pendidikan | Sebuah Pengantar&nbsp;</a></li><li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/62yZre64t3o\">Literasi Sebagai Sarana Stimulasi Perkembangan – Sutarimah Ampuni, M.Si., M.Psych, Psikolog&nbsp;</a></li><li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/1K7C5ididW8\">Filsafat Psikologi dan Pandangan Hidup Manusia (Belajar Psikologi)&nbsp;</a></li><li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/18dN9LJOpCU\">Ngaji Filsafat 215 : Abraham Maslow – Kepribadian (Filsafat Manusia)&nbsp;</a></li><li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/bQHTS02BLtM\">Penguatan Pendidikan Karakter di Masa Pandemi Covid-19&nbsp;</a></li><li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/w0GJFa5oZKY\">Apakah Kepribadian dan Sifat Manusia Bisa Diubah? (Bela